PORT "API port"
DB_PATH "location of your database"
API "url to this api"
SECRET "to sign the jwt"
IMDB_USER_AGENT "realistic browser User-Agent for IMDB GraphQL requests"
IMDB_TIMEOUT "ms for IMDB HTTP requests (e.g. 15000)"
IMDB_GRAPHQL_ENDPOINT "override the IMDB GraphQL endpoint (default https://api.graphql.imdb.com/)"
IMDB_TZ "timezone used to decide if an episode already aired (default: system tz, e.g. America/Mexico_City)"
RSS_USER_AGENT "User-Agent for RSS/Atom feed fetches (e.g. MangaCafeRSS/1.0)"
RSS_TIMEOUT "ms for RSS HTTP requests (e.g. 15000)"
